OL,3,COrganised criminal gangs recruiting
OL,4,CHGV drivers to smuggle migrants
OL,6,FOrganised criminal gangs are actively
OL,7,Frecruiting HGV drivers to smuggle
OL,8,Fmigrants both into and out of the UK.
OL,10,FThe National Crime Agency says there
OL,11,Fhas been a spike in arrests in Kent
OL,12,Fwhich has seen a number of drivers
OL,13,Fdetained as they attempted to board
OL,14,Ftrains or ferries to France whilst
OL,15,Fcarrying people illegally in their
OL,16,Fvehicles.
