OL,3,COrganised criminal gangs recruiting
OL,4,CHGV drivers to smuggle migrants
OL,6,FThe NCA warns people smugglers are
OL,7,Fknown to be targeting drivers,
OL,8,Foffering them thousands of pounds to
OL,9,Ftransport people across the border in
OL,10,Fotherwise legitimate loads.
OL,12,FIn some cases drivers are known to
OL,13,Fhave assisted the criminal gangs in
OL,14,Floading people into their trucks, in
OL,15,Fothers they have turned a blind eye by
OL,16,Fleaving their vehicles unlocked in
OL,17,Fspecific locations.
