OL,3,COrganised criminal gangs recruiting
OL,4,CHGV drivers to smuggle migrants
OL,6,FNCA Deputy Director of Investigations
OL,7,FCraig Turner said: "We know these
OL,8,Fcrime gangs are actively trying to
OL,9,Frecruit drivers to work for them,
OL,10,Fpromising them a supposedly low risk
OL,11,Fway of making extra money.
OL,13,F"In fact, it is anything but. We have
OL,14,Fa number of operations investigating
OL,15,Fthis type of criminality, and recent
OL,16,Farrests have demonstrated that the
OL,17,Fchances of getting caught are high.
OL,19,F"Those who do get caught risk a life-
OL,20,Fchanging prison sentence. It simply
OL,21,Fisn't worth the risk.
