OL,3,COrganised criminal gangs recruiting
OL,4,CHGV drivers to smuggle migrants
OL,6,F"I'm certain that the overwhelming
OL,7,Fmajority of those in the haulage
OL,8,Findustry are law abiding and I would
OL,9,Furge them to report any suspicious
OL,10,Factivity like this to the police or
OL,11,FCrimestoppers."
OL,13,FBetween July and October this year the
OL,14,FNCA said it has been involved in the
OL,15,Farrests of nine lorry drivers in Kent
OL,16,Ffor people smuggling offences.
