OL,6,FIona Monescu, 49, from Romania, was
OL,7,Fdetained after 44 Bangladeshi and
OL,8,FPakistani people were found in the
OL,9,Fback of his trailer at the port of
OL,10,FDover in August. He was sentenced to
OL,11,Fthree years in prison on 25 September.
OL,13,FThe NCA said it is continuing to carry
OL,14,Fout a number of investigations looking
OL,15,Fat criminal groups using trucks to
OL,16,Fsmuggle people.
