OL,3,COrganised criminal gangs recruiting
OL,4,CHGV drivers to smuggle migrants
OL,6,FOn 17 July this year seven members of
OL,7,Fa people smuggling network were jailed
OL,8,Ffor between 13 and seven years each
OL,9,Ffor organising crossings from the UK
OL,10,Fto France. Five HGV drivers were also
OL,11,Fjailed for their roles in assisting
OL,12,Fthe gang.
OL,14,FAnd in June 2023 people smuggling boss
OL,15,FMd Moktar Hossain, from Woodford
OL,16,FGreen, London, was jailed for more
OL,17,Fthan ten years. The NCA investigation
OL,18,Finto his crime group saw seven lorry
OL,19,Fdrivers convicted and sent to prison.
