OL,3,COrganised criminal gangs recruiting
OL,4,CHGV drivers to smuggle migrants
OL,6,FAnother group investigated by the NCA
OL,7,Fface trial in January for allegedly
OL,8,Fsmuggling Afghan migrants to the UK in
OL,9,Fthe back of a lorry. The vehicle's
OL,10,Fdriver is among those charged.
OL,12,FDeputy Director Craig Turner said:
OL,13,F"The criminal networks offering
OL,14,Fservices to move people out of the UK
OL,15,Fillegally are often using the same
OL,16,Fdrivers and methods to bring people
OL,17,Fin, which makes it more important that
OL,18,Fwe take action against them.
