OL,3,COrganised criminal gangs recruiting
OL,4,CHGV drivers to smuggle migrants
OL,6,F"For them, this is a business, and
OL,7,Flike any other haulier they don't want
OL,8,Fto 'run empty' while returning to the
OL,9,Fcontinent.
OL,11,F"Tackling organised immigration crime
OL,12,Fis a key priority for the NCA. We have
OL,13,Faround 100 investigations ongoing into
OL,14,Fgroups or individuals involved in the
OL,15,Ftop tier of this form of criminality,
OL,16,Fand we are determined to do all we can
OL,17,Fto target, disrupt and dismantle them."
