OL,6,FThe NCA, alongside Border Force and
OL,7,Fthe charity Crimestoppers, launched a
OL,8,Fcampaign in 2023 appealing to those
OL,9,Fworking in the haulage industry to
OL,10,Fstay alert and report suspicious
OL,11,Factivity.
OL,13,FThose with information can contact
OL,14,FCrimestoppers anonymously on 0800
OL,15,F555111, or online via their website.
